X3M Music artiste, Praiz, has released the visuals of his hit song, ‘Here and Now’. Directed by Ani James of Aje Filmworks, the video has been described by pundits as oozing of greatness. A highly captivating video, ‘Here and Now’ is one on of the songs off Praiz’ latest body of work titled ‘2 Minutes The EP’. Since the award-winning singer joined the music industry, the young man doesn’t want to take the back seat when it comes to Rand B music. The singer has not stopped dishing out the best soul-touching music, which has got more fans endeared to him. Just back from an international travel tour, Praiz is melting hearts again with his music. 